If the new `VPInstruction` has opcode `Instruction::And` (from `(x && y) | (x && z) -> x && (y | z)`), `VPInstruction::execute` handles `Instruction::isBinaryOp(getOpcode())` by calling `Builder.CreateBinOp`.
